c payment card used in the purchase process, especially if the card used in the payment process is issued by a foreign bank .Also, the company has the right to cancel the purchase request if the customer refuses to do so.<br><br>→ELARABY Group is not responsible for any banking transactions between the customer and his bank, and ELARABY’s role is limited to requiring the bank to pay the amount due. In the case of non-payment, ELARABY Group has the right to cancel the customer’s purchase without consulting the customer.<br><br>→The customer registers the purchase request himself through our website and shows him the purchase order number after completing all the steps successfully and during the registration of the purchase request, the customer chooses the date for executing the order according to the dates available for execution on the website during the registration of the request, and an email is sent to the customer with the details of the purchase request, also a message is sent to the customer on the phone number registered with the application stating the order number, and the customer is contacted in case of need to complete the data before confirming the order, and we have the right to cancel the purchase request at any time in the case that we were not able to reach the customer. Also, the delivery process takes place at the address registered in the purchase order only and at the time specified by the customer during the registration of the purchase request, and the customer’s receipt of the product is an acknowledgment from him that the product has been carefully examined and ensured that it is in good condition, free from any defects and with all its contents, and in the case that the customer wants to install the device by our company, he will call the customer service 19319 to register an installation notification, in the case of devices that need a technician from the company to install them, and during the call of the registration, the customer wil